<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <main id="main-content">
      <section class="hero section-band">
        <div class="page-shell hero-grid">
          <div class="hero-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">JC2503 Coursework Website</p>
            <h1>AptS:1547</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Computer Science student and web application developer</p>
            <p class="hero-text">
              I am interested in practical web applications, open-source tools, and interactive systems. This coursework website introduces my background, explains the structure of the site, and provides access to the multiplayer 4x4 puzzle game built for the assignment.
            </p>
            <nav class="hero-actions" aria-label="Primary page links">
              <a class="button primary" href="/about">Explore About</a>
              <a class="button secondary" href="/game">Open Game</a>
            </nav>
          </div>

          <aside class="profile-panel" aria-label="Profile summary">
            <img
              class="avatar"
              src="/images/avatar.png"
              alt="My original character AptS:1547"
            >
            <dl class="profile-facts">
              <div>
                <dt>Study</dt>
                <dd>Computer Science</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt>Focus</dt>
                <dd>Web applications and developer tools</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt>Coursework</dt>
                <dd>JC2503 Web Application Development</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="page-shell content-section">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">Website Overview</p>
          <h2>Three pages, one consistent structure</h2>
          <p>
            This site is organised around a short introduction, a more detailed about page, and an interactive puzzle game page.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-grid three-columns">
          <article class="feature-card">
            <span class="card-kicker">01</span>
            <h3>Introduction</h3>
            <p>
              A concise landing page with personal context, study information, and links to the main sections of the site.
            </p>
            <a class="card-link" href="/">View introduction</a>
          </article>

          <article class="feature-card accent-cyan">
            <span class="card-kicker">02</span>
            <h3>About</h3>
            <p>
              A more detailed page about my study background, personal interests, and the areas I want to develop further.
            </p>
            <a class="card-link" href="/about">Read about me</a>
          </article>

          <article class="feature-card accent-green">
            <span class="card-kicker">03</span>
            <h3>Game Application</h3>
            <p>
              A browser-based 4x4 puzzle game page where multiple players will join, take turns, place blocks, and follow the scoreboard.
            </p>
            <a class="card-link" href="/game">Open game page</a>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
